      "file_path": "bpmn/MSOCommonBPMN/src/main/java/org/onap/so/client/cds/GeneratePayloadForCds.java",
      "patchset_number": 10,
      "line": 97,
      "message": "To be honest I still don't understand why you need to use this class if you could add this implementation to GenericCDSProcessingDE which is focused solely on PNFs. Now you need to add more string-based 'cases' and 'ifs' which are later very difficult to find by other developers. I know how much time it took me to find all those VNF/PNF related implementations hidden all over the SO code in similar 'cases' and 'ifs'. Anyway this is just a comment, if you feel this better suits your needs then I won't argue here.",
