      "patchset_number": 10,
      "line": 44,
      "message": "This class is only serve legacy config related cases i.e. when config-assign and config-deploy fetch ip-addresses from aai. \n\nIn upcoming actions this is not the case. If any action needs any parameter from aai, CDS has capability to fetch it directly from AAI. \n\nIMO, this class will be removed in future. \n\nI'll change the name anyway.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5006,
        "name": "Rahul Tyagi",
        "display_name": "Rahul Tyagi",
        "email": "rahul.tyagi@est.tech",
